<p>This Privacy Policy describes how The Guilded Gauge ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you use KnitConvert ("the App"). We are committed to being transparent about our data practices and protecting your privacy. By using the App you also agree to our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>.</p>

<hr class="divider">

<h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
<p>The Guilded Gauge is an independent app studio. KnitConvert is our first product. You can contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@theguildedgauge.app">hello@theguildedgauge.app</a> with any privacy-related questions.</p>

<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect only what is necessary to provide the service.</p>
<p><strong>Pattern content</strong> — Patterns you paste or import are processed entirely on-device to perform gauge conversion. Pattern content is never transmitted to or stored on our servers. This is intentional — we respect the copyright of pattern designers and publishers.</p>
<p><strong>Account information</strong> — If you create an account, we collect your email address and a hashed password via Supabase, our authentication provider.</p>
<p><strong>Gauge and swatch data</strong> — Measurement data you enter is used locally on your device to perform conversions.</p>
<p><strong>Subscription information</strong> — Subscription status and purchase history are managed by RevenueCat. We do not store payment card details.</p>
<p><strong>AI lookups</strong> — When you use the AI abbreviation lookup feature, your query is sent to the Anthropic Claude API for processing. Queries are not stored by us beyond the active session.</p>
<p><strong>Usage data</strong> — We may collect anonymised, aggregated usage analytics to improve the App. This data cannot be used to identify you personally.</p>

<h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>To provide and improve the gauge conversion service</li>
  <li>To manage your account and subscription</li>
  <li>To process AI-powered abbreviation lookups</li>
  <li>To respond to support requests</li>
  <li>To send important service updates (not marketing, unless you opt in)</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We use the following third-party services to operate KnitConvert. Each acts as a data processor under our instruction:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Authentication and database. <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
  <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> — Subscription and purchase management. <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
  <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude API)</strong> — AI-powered abbreviation lookups. <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
</ul>
<p>We do not sell your data to third parties. We do not use your data for advertising purposes.</p>

<h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>Your account data is stored securely via Supabase on servers located in the United States. We use industry-standard encryption for data in transit and at rest. Pattern content processed locally on your device is not transmitted to our servers.</p>

<h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain your account data for as long as your account is active. You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@theguildedgauge.app">hello@theguildedgauge.app</a>. We will action deletion requests within 30 days.</p>

<h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
<p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
  <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
  <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
  <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
  <li>Data portability</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@theguildedgauge.app">hello@theguildedgauge.app</a>.</p>

<h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>KnitConvert is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>

<h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes via the App or by email. The date at the top of this page reflects the most recent update.</p>

<h2>10. Contact</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@theguildedgauge.app">hello@theguildedgauge.app</a>.</p>
